{"type":"message","id":"35a9c2a3","parentId":"ae47409b","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:30:00.064Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:75e0873c-760b-4dc2-8b7d-bac71e6f89bc a-stock-morning-15min] 【严重】禁止使用浏览器！只使用QVeris获取数据！执行步骤：1)调用QVeris的ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1获取002149.SZ,601899.SH,601975.SH实时股价；2)调用QVeris获取上证指数000001.SH；3)直接输出结果，不要打开任何浏览器或网页。如果QVeris失败，返回'数据获取失败'。\nCurrent time: Wednesday, March 4th, 2026 — 11:30 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772595000063}}
{"type":"message","id":"94e2c49e","parentId":"35a9c2a3","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:30:06.968Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to get real-time stock data using QVeris. Let me follow the steps:\n1. Get real-time quotes for 002149.SZ, 601899.SH, 601975.SH\n2. Get Shanghai Composite Index 000001.SH\n3. Output the results directly\n\nLet me use the qveris-official skill first to understand how to use it, then make the calls.","thinkingSignature":"ee73aa72d115202b0f2822f1852a3f571028b02d4753f6c53d8e901d12cd4f5d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wn74l4xblt5l_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"qveris-official","mode":"run","task":"获取以下股票的实时行情数据：\n1. 002149.SZ\n2. 601899.SH  \n3. 601975.SH\n4. 上证指数 000001.SH\n\n请调用ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1接口获取这些数据，返回实时股价信息。"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":196,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":14136,"totalTokens":14368,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772595000064}}
