, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 780.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.914\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"aebff975-4fbe-4360-95ec-327ab9c3b800\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 170.9\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772595337144}}
